# Language: English only

All source files, documentation, and user-facing content in this project must be written in **English**.

- Code: comments, docstrings, variable/function names (when not domain-specific), log messages.
- Docs: README files, inline documentation, commit messages.
- Exception: strings or content that are intentionally in another language for business or locale reasons (e.g. UI copy for a specific locale).

When adding or editing files, use English. When translating existing content (e.g. READMEs), replace the previous language with English.
